
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "AboutUs";
    Layout = "~/Views/Shared/_Layout.cshtml";
}

<div class="container-fluid">
    <div class="row px-xl-5">
        <div class="col-12">
            <nav class="breadcrumb bg-light mb-30">
                <a class="breadcrumb-item text-dark" asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Index">Home</a>
                <span class="breadcrumb-item active">About Us</span>
            </nav>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="container">
   
    <div class="about-us">
        <h4 class=" mx-xl-5 mb-4">
            Welcome to MULTI SHOP, your premier destination for online shopping convenience!<br />
            Founded with the vision of providing customers with a seamless and enjoyable shopping experience, we strive to offer a wide range of products coupled with excellent customer service.
        </h4>

        <p class="mx-xl-5 mb-4">
            At MULTI SHOP, we understand the importance of simplicity and efficiency when it comes to fulfilling your shopping needs. Our user-friendly interface allows you to effortlessly browse through our extensive selection of products, compare prices, and make informed purchasing decisions from the comfort of your own home.
        </p>

        <p class="mx-xl-5 mb-4">
            With a dedicated team of professionals, we ensure that every aspect of your online shopping journey is smooth and hassle-free. Whether you're searching for everyday essentials or specialty items, we have you covered.
        </p>

        <p class="mx-xl-5 mb-4">
            Our commitment to customer satisfaction extends beyond just offering great products. We also provide various offers and discounts to help you save money on your purchases. Additionally, our prompt delivery service ensures that your orders reach you in a timely manner, allowing you to enjoy your products without delay.
        </p>

        <p class="mx-xl-5 mb-4">
            As part of our dedication to transparency, we provide detailed information about our products, including images and features, to help you make the right choice. Moreover, we welcome your feedback and encourage you to rate and review products, helping us continually improve our offerings.
        </p>

        <p class="mx-xl-5 mb-4">
            For any inquiries or assistance, our customer support team is always available to help. Simply reach out to us via phone, email, or our online chat feature, and we'll be happy to assist you.
        </p>

        <p class="mx-xl-5 mb-4">
            Thank you for choosing MULTI SHOP for your online shopping needs. We look forward to serving you and exceeding your expectations every step of the way. Happy shopping!
        </p>
    </div>
    
</div>

<style>
    .about-us {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

        .about-us h4 {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .about-us p {
            font-size: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
</style>